== 0.4 ==

Release Date : *December 4th, 2009*

  * Major rewrites of core systems
  * Nomenclature fixes
  * Twig Integration
  * RSS Support
  * Tagbox system for templates
  * Rewrite of the URL subsystem
  * URL Extension mapping to Format
  * Maintenance Mode
  * User Listings
  * Support for mapping models to multiple tables
  * Font functionality
